《'''男子漢'''》是香港歌手[[李龍基|李龍基]]發行第五張粵語專輯，於1982年6月7日由[[EMI|EMI百代]]發行。<ref>[https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/顧嘉煇系列13-男子漢-另一警匪片歌曲經典-fbb5b77d992c] {{Wayback|url=https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/%E9%A1%A7%E5%98%89%E7%85%87%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%9713-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%BC%A2-%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%8C%AA%E7%89%87%E6%AD%8C%E6%9B%B2%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8-fbb5b77d992c |date=20210716124725 }}、[https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=fdyVDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA208&lpg=PA208&dq=李龍基+男子漢+大碟&source=bl&ots=T01MC6wgba&sig=ACfU3U2LabMS3lqFrLwNodw8vNblr_PV-w&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjjrcP03N3xAhVBQfUHHXZPAQw4MhDoATAJegQIBxAC#v=onepage&q=李龍基%20男子漢%20大碟&f=false] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=fdyVDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA208&lpg=PA208&dq=%E6%9D%8E%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%BA+%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%BC%A2+%E5%A4%A7%E7%A2%9F&source=bl&ots=T01MC6wgba&sig=ACfU3U2LabMS3lqFrLwNodw8vNblr_PV-w&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjjrcP03N3xAhVBQfUHHXZPAQw4MhDoATAJegQIBxAC#v=onepage&q=李龍基%20男子漢%20大碟&f=false |date=20210715135735 }}、[https://www.discogs.com/李龍基-男子漢/release/14002483] {{Wayback|url=https://www.discogs.com/%E6%9D%8E%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%BA-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%BC%A2/release/14002483 |date=20210712142724 }}</ref>

== 解說 ==
專輯的同名曲為[[無綫電視|無綫電視]][[翡翠台|翡翠台]]的[[男子漢_(電視劇)|同名劇集]]主題曲<ref>{{cite website |url=https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/song/Zl9VqiS022P5H80VF80VF0P4-index.html |title=男子漢 - 無綫電視劇「男子漢」主題曲 |website=[[KKBOX|KKBOX]] |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2021-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715232341/https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/song/Zl9VqiS022P5H80VF80VF0P4-index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。歌曲使用了[[管弦樂|管弦樂]]與[[電結他|電結他]]作為伴奏<ref name="medium">{{cite website |url=https://medium.com/@michaelchu_73917/顧嘉煇系列13-男子漢-另一警匪片歌曲經典-fbb5b77d992c |title=【顧嘉煇系列13】《男子漢》另一警匪片歌曲經典 |author=千千闋歌與我常在 |website=Medium |date=2018-10-01 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209114816/https://medium.com/@michaelchu_73917/%E9%A1%A7%E5%98%89%E7%85%87%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%9713-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%BC%A2-%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%8C%AA%E7%89%87%E6%AD%8C%E6%9B%B2%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8-fbb5b77d992c |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並以男子氣慨作為歌詞主題<ref name="medium"/>。

收錄曲《稻草人》獲得極大成功<ref>{{cite website |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/20180617-118669 |title=【同皇帝撞名】深宮計李龍基vs李隆基　TVB御用皇帝由寵幸Do姐開始 |website=[[明報周刊|明報周刊]] |date=2018-06-17 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2021-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713134906/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/focus/20180617-118669 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並讓[[李龍基|李龍基]]成為「酒廊王子」<ref name="we">{{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=v0_aDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA109|title=我們都是這樣唱大的|author=[[區瑞強|區瑞強]]|location=香港|work=知出版社|publisher=香港聯合書刊物流有限公司|ISBN=9789621460646|page=109|date=2016-10-07|accessdate=2019-12-09|archive-date=2021-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713134904/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=v0_aDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA109|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為他於酒廊最受客人歡迎的演唱曲<ref name="we"/>。

